\s Sisi huku si matajiri, kwani miaka yapita 
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Sisi huku si matajiri, kwani miaka yapita. Mara nyingi twapata shida, kwani miaka yapita. Tukimwamini \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  na kumtumikia, tutapata thawabu, kwani miaka yapita. \bd*
\pc \bdit Yapita, yapita, yapita, yapita, tumikieni \bdit*\bdit Mwokozi\bdit*\bdit , kwani miaka yapita. \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Hatutaogopa kitu, kwani miaka yapita. Bali tutafurahi tu, kwani miaka yapita. Dunia ni shida, mashaka na huzuni. Bali tukaze mwendo, kwani miaka yapita. \bd*
\pc \bdit Yapita, yapita, yapita, yapita, tumikieni \bdit*\bdit Mwokozi\bdit*\bdit , kwani miaka yapita. \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Rafiki wanatuacha, kwani miaka yapita. Na safari itaisha, kwani miaka yapita. Tupande mbegu njema, rohoni mwa wenzetu, wengine waokoke, kwani miaka yapita. \bd*
\pc \bdit Yapita, yapita, yapita, yapita, tumikieni \bdit*\bdit Mwokozi\bdit*\bdit , kwani miaka yapita. \bdit*
